channel.title: Suggestions to sources
channel.description: I want a good server, I wanna know what you guys think. I am going to be hosting! Can you guys post ur favorite sources. I cant find any good ones. Please and thanks!

item.title: Suggestions to sources
item.dc:creator: @Fridder Fridder
item.description:
@Fridder wrote:

If your 100% new to RSPS, use AllstarScape - not the best stability, but it will help you learn the basic things. Then move onto a basic PI server, not one of the crappy DSPK servers. Yeah, 525 graphics could [size=3pt](and probably will)[/size] get you a lot of [size=1pt]dumb[/size]players, but it will lag a lot and all sources that lag are shit.
